@echo off\nREM FreeAutotune Build Script for Windows\n\necho FreeAutotune Build Script\necho ==========================\necho.\n\nREM Check if JUCE submodule exists\nif not exist \"JUCE\" (\n    echo Adding JUCE submodule...\n    git submodule add https://github.com/juce-framework/JUCE.git\n)\n\nREM Create build directory\nif not exist \"build\" (\n    mkdir build\n)\n\ncd build\n\necho Generating build files...\ncmake -G \"Visual Studio 16 2019\" ..\n\necho Building FreeAutotune...\ncmake --build . --config Release\n\necho.\necho Build complete!\necho.\necho Plugin location:\necho   VST3: .\\FreeAutotune_artefacts\\Release\\VST3\\\necho.\necho To install:\necho   Copy to: C:\\Program Files\\Common Files\\VST3\\\necho.\npause\n"